<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>First Stop: Right to Privacy in the Workplace Act</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#004080" LINK="#004080" VLINK="#0080C0" ALINK="#0080C0">

<img src="/dcca/graph/fs/fslogosm.gif" alt="First Stop Logo" width=171 height=120 align=left>
<h3 align=center>Department of Commerce & Community Affairs
<hr>
First Stop Business Information Center<br>
Business Requirement
</h3>
<hr>
<br clear=all>

<H3>I.	Business Requirement Profile:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Right to Privacy in the Workplace Act
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>II.	Agency:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Illinois Department of Labor<BR>
Fair Labor Standards Division<BR>
160 N. LaSalle <BR>
Chicago, IL 60601<BR>
(312) 793-1805<BR>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>III.	Statute:</H3>
<DL><DD>
820 Illinois Compiled Statutes 55/1-20
</DD></DL>
<H3>Regulation:</H3>
<DL><DD>
56 Illinois Administrative Code 360.100 to 360.180 
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>IV:	Requirement Description:</H3>
<DL><DD>
The Act prohibits employers from discharging or otherwise retaliating against employees or prospective employees for their use of lawful products outside the workplace during nonworking hours. The Act prohibits employers from making inquiries about claims filed by prospective employees under the Worker's Compensation Act or the Worker's Occupational Disease Act.<P>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>V.	Approval Process:</H3>
<DL><DD>
None.
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>VI.	Pre-Requisites, Co-Requisites & Post-Requisites:</H3>
<DL><DD>
An aggrieved employee may file a complaint with the Department alleging that he or she has been denied  rights protected under the Act. The Act authorizes the Department to investigate the complaint and to "attempt to resolve the complaint by conference, conciliation, or persuasion."  The Department may compel an employer to comply with the Act by a civil action. An aggrieved employee may file a private suit upon notice from the Department that the agency has concluded its enforcement efforts and will take no further action on the matter.<P>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>VII.	Fees:</H3>
<DL><DD>
None.
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<STRONG>| <a href="/dcca/home.htm">DCCA Home Page</a> | <A HREF="/dcca/menus/fsm1.htm">First Stop</a> | <A HREF="/dcca/menus/fsbr.htm">Business Requirements</a> |</STRONG>

