New licensees will receive an infomative packet which will include the Illinois Liquor Control Act, Rules and Regulations, educational booklets and all required signage.  Licensees are encouraged to review this information carefully as it contains information which will assist you in complying with Illinois liquor laws.<P>
</DD></DL>

