<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>First Stop: Annual Oil & Gas Operators Fee </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#004080" LINK="#004080" VLINK="#0080C0" ALINK="#0080C0">

<img src="/dcca/graph/fs/fslogosm.gif" alt="First Stop Logo" width=171 height=120 align=left>
<h3 align=center>Department of Commerce & Community Affairs
<hr>
First Stop Business Information Center<br>
Business Requirement
</h3>
<hr>
<br clear=all>

<H3>I.   Business Requirement Profile:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Annual Oil & Gas Operators Fee 
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>II.  Agency:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Illinois Department of Natural Resources<BR>
Oil & Gas Division<BR>
300 West Jefferson St. - Suite 300<BR>
P.O. Box 10137<BR>
Springfield, IL 62791-0137<BR>
(217) 782-7756<BR>
TDD:  (217) 524-4626 <BR>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>III. Statute:</H3>
<DL><DD>
225 Illinois Compiled Statute 725/19.7
</DD></DL>
<H3>Regulation:</H3>
<DL><DD>
62 Illinois Administrative Code 240.1700-1740 <P>
62 Illinois Administrative Code 240.1710
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>IV.	Requirement Description:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Oil and gas operators are required to pay an annual well fee based upon the total number of wells owned as of July 1 of each year. <P>

Failure to pay annual well fees results in enforcement action by the Department including an order to cease production and assessment of civil penalties.<P>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>V. 	Approval Process:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Applicants must file an "Annual Fee Status Report & Address Verification Form", form #OG-1, and applicable fees to the Department by September 1 of each year. If any information is lacking on the form or the fee is incorrect, the applicant will be contacted by the Department.   Department enforcement actions are subject to administrative review. <P>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>VI. 	Pre-Requisites, Co-Requisites & Post-Requisites:</H3>
<DL><DD>
None.
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>VII. Fees:  </H3>
<DL><DD>
There are no application fees but well fees are:<P>

	1 well:			$150<BR>
	2 -5 wells:		$300<BR>
	6 - 25 wells:		$750<BR>
	26 - 100 wells:		$1,500<BR>
	101 + wells:		$1,500 + $12.50 / each additional well<BR>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<STRONG>| <a href="/dcca/home.htm">DCCA Home Page</a> | <A HREF="/dcca/menus/fsm1.htm">First Stop</a> | <A HREF="/dcca/menus/fsbr.htm">Business Requirements</a> |</STRONG>

</BODY>
</HTML>
