<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>First Stop: Permit for Lease Road Oiling</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#004080" LINK="#004080" VLINK="#0080C0" ALINK="#0080C0">

<img src="/dcca/graph/fs/fslogosm.gif" alt="First Stop Logo" width=171 height=120 align=left>
<h3 align=center>Department of Commerce & Community Affairs
<hr>
First Stop Business Information Center<br>
Business Requirement
</h3>
<hr>
<br clear=all>

<H3>I.   Business Requirement Profile:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Permit for Lease Road Oiling
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>II.  Agency:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Illinois Department of Natural Resources<BR>
Office of Mines & Minerals  (OMM)<BR>
Oil & Gas Division<BR>
524 South Second Street<BR>
Springfield, IL 62701-1787<BR>
(217) 782-7756<BR>
TDD:  (217) 524-4626 <BR>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>III. Statute:</H3>
<DL><DD>
225 Illinois Compiled Statutes 725/6
</DD></DL>
<H3>Regulation:</H3>
<DL><DD>
62 Illinois Administrative Code 240.940(b)
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>IV.	Requirement Description:</H3>
<DL><DD>
A Permit is required to Oil-Lease roads with crude oil tank bottom sediments. The Permit authorizes oiling and remains valid until the oil lease owner or surface landowner changes.<P>

Oiling a lease road without a Permit may result in enforcement action, including civil penalties.<P>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>V.  	Approval Process:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Applicants must submit an "Application for Lease Road Oiling", Form #OG-2, notarized by the landowner.<P>

Review, approval and permit issuance generally takes 3 to 5 days. <P>

Lease roads may be oiled only twice a year with bottom sediments produced on that Lease. <P>

Oil-Lease roads may not be oiled when the ground is frozen.  Applied oil and sediments are required to be incorporated into the road surface with no runoff or free standing liquid. Department decisions are subject to administrative review.<P>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>VI. 	Pre-Requisites, Co-Requisites & Post-Requisites:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Applicants for a Permit must be the operator of the Oil Lease Road to be oiled.<P>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>VII. Fees:</H3>
<DL><DD>
None.
</DD></DL>


<HR>
<STRONG>| <a href="/dcca/home.htm">DCCA Home Page</a> | <A HREF="/dcca/menus/fsm1.htm">First Stop</a> | <A HREF="/dcca/menus/fsbr.htm">Business Requirements</a> |</STRONG>

</BODY>
