<HEAD><TITLE>First Stop: MPEA (Metropolitan Pier Exposition Authority) Automobile Rental Tax</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#004080" LINK="#004080" VLINK="#0080C0" ALINK="#0080C0">

<img src="/dcca/graph/fs/fslogosm.gif" alt="First Stop Logo" width=171 height=120 align=left>
<h3 align=center>Department of Commerce & Community Affairs
<hr>
First Stop Business Information Center<br>
Business Requirement
</h3>
<hr>
<br clear=all>

<H3>I.	Business Requirement Profile:	</H3>
<DL><DD>MPEA (Metropolitan Pier Exposition Authority) Automobile Rental Tax</DD></DL>
<HR>
<H3>II.	Agency: </H3>
<DL><DD>Illinois Department of Revenue<BR>
101 W. Jefferson<BR>
Springfield, IL 62794<BR>
Taxpayer Services Bureau<BR>
Central Registration Division<BR>
(217) 785-3707</DD></DL>
<HR>
<H3>III.	Statute:  </H3>
<DL><DD>70 Illinois Compiled Statutes 210/13d</DD></DL>
<HR>
<H3>IV.	Requirement Description: </H3>
<DL><DD><P>The MPEA imposes a tax on businesses that rent or lease automobiles or certain recreational vehicles or vans for periods of one year or less from a business located in Cook County.  Businesses must complete and file with the Department an application for a certificate authorizing collection and remittance of the MPEA Automobile Rental Tax.

<P>Failure to register with the Department and to collect and remit these taxes may result in penalties that include, but are not limited to:  A tax lien against property, garnishment of wages and bank accounts, revocation of professional licenses, civil judgments, revocation of business certificates of registration, withholding of state warrants, seizure and sale of assets, nonrenewal of corporate charter and/or criminal prosecution.  A certificate of registration is valid for 5 years. If a registered business remains in compliance, the Department will automatically issue a renewal.</DD></DL>
<HR>
<H3>V.	Approval Process:  </H3>
<DL><DD>Applicants must complete and file with the Department an Automobile Renting Registration Application (NUC-1A).  Applications are processed in about 3 weeks.</DD></DL>
<HR>
<H3>VI.	Pre-Requisites, Co-Requisites & Post-Requisites:  </H3>
<DL><DD>A Federal Employer Identification Number (FEIN) may be required</DD></DL>
<HR>
<H3>VII.	Fees: </H3>
<DL><DD>There is no registration fee.</DD></DL>

<HR>
