<CENTER><H3>Coal Development Program</H3></CENTER>
<HR>
<H4>
DCCA provides funds to advance promising new coal research
technologies through the proof-of-concept state to the commercial
demonstration stage. Development processes include technology
maturation, technology transfer and related studies.  Priorities for
this program are established by tracking key market issues and
projecting ways technology can take advantage of these issues to
locate new markets for Illinois coal.<P>

For information call 217/785-2017.<P>
