<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>DCCA: Just for Kids -- Coal is Cool!</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#0000A0" LINK="#0000A0" VLINK="#800080" ALINK="#800080">

<img src="../graph/logosm.jpg" alt="DCCA Logo" width=165 height=82 align=left>
<img src="../graph/cbar.gif" width=410 height=4><p>
<h3>
Department of Commerce & Community Affairs<p>
</h3>
<img src="../graph/cbar.gif" width=410 height=4><p>


<img src="../graph/coalcool.jpg" width=221 height=308 align=right>

<h3>
<img src="../graph/button1.gif" width=27 height=34 align=middle> <a href="../files/kids/ilcoal.htm"> Coal and Illinois</a><p>
<img src="../graph/button1.gif" width=27 height=34 align=middle> <a href="../files/kids/coalfact.htm"> Illinois Coal Fact Sheet</a><p>
<img src="../graph/button1.gif" width=27 height=34 align=middle> <a href="../files/kids/mining.htm"> Mining Coal</a><p>
<img src="../graph/button1.gif" width=27 height=34 align=middle> <a href="../files/kids/miners.htm"> Miners</a><p>
<img src="../graph/button1.gif" width=27 height=34 align=middle> <a href="../files/kids/uses.htm"> Uses of Coal</a><p>
<img src="../graph/button1.gif" width=27 height=34 align=middle> <a href="../files/kids/landrec.htm"> Land Reclamation</a><p>
<img src="../graph/button1.gif" width=27 height=34 align=middle> <a href="../files/kids/newtech.htm"> New Technologies</a><p>
