<a name="Advisory Council"><hr></a>
<h3>Advisory Council</h3>

The department established and maintains an advisory council to guide in its state administration of the CSBG program.  This council provides invaluable policy making advice through its broad mix of statewide representation.<p>

For additional information, call the State of Illinois Department of Commerce and Community Affairs, Community Services Block Grant Program at 217/785-6156; TDD, 800/785-6055.  All programs may be accessed through the State TDD Relay; 800/526-0844.<p>

