<h3>Eligibility</h3>

State-supported colleges and universities<p>

<h3>Funding</h3>

Funding is provided through a grant process.  Separate funding assistance is available for both development of the waste reduction plans and for implementation of activities outlined in approved waste reduction plans.  Supportable categories for implementation grants include collection, processing, composting and source reduction.  Maximum eligible amount of funding is dependent upon full time equivalent student population.<p>

